commit 64eb603802ca094b2a6f82ef881da5cdd69fad9c
Author: GIAN MARC DOMALANTA <giandomalanta22@gmail.com>
Date:   Wed Jun 24 15:11:23 2026 +0800

    feat(ui): unify boundary and watershed panels, fix state logic, and enhance map interactions
    
    • Fixed state execution bugs to ensure the side panel properly updates and explicitly closes when toggling between Watershed and Boundary modes.
    • Unified UI design and information architecture across both panels, standardizing green hero card dimensions, metrics containers, padding, and hierarchical list layouts.
    • Corrected text casing issues, enforcing standard Title Case for UI lists and Leaflet map tooltips.
    • Resolved case-insensitive string matching bugs to fully restore click-to-zoom and active state functionality for province selection.
    • Repaired the boundary map highlight styles to successfully apply the dashed red outline on active selections without overwriting global layer styles or stacking colors.
    • Fixed boundary layer hover (mouseover) glitches to preserve boundary stroke weights, ensuring proper legend color restoration on mouseout.
    • Updated panel instructional copy for better user clarity and adjusted vertical spacing for list cards.

